name: MyPersonalTrainer
0:
”Alexa, ask My Personal Trainer if I'm going running today.”
”Alexa, ask My Personal Trainer how far I should run.”
”Alexa, ask My Personal Trainer should I run?”
skdetail:
This skill contains: dynamic content.
Invocation Name: my personal trainer
des: Ask your personal trainer if you're going running today. Immediately, she encourages you to work out and provides you with a motivational quote. Note: this app does not provide medical or fitness advice. Always consult your doctor before beginning any workout regimen.
priv: The developer reported that this skill does not collect personal information.
